file_content.text: They're all dead? What did you do in here...?
Forget that. You're amazing. Did they hurt you?
The assassins are finished. Don't think they'll tell us much, though.
Situation handled.
Not in their condition.
Don't worry about me.
I thought you were hiding back in town?
Where'd you come from?
What? No--I wanted to make sure you were okay.
You look--never mind. If you hadn't stopped them, they would've come after me. I don't know how to thank you.
I don't need gratitude. Let's just get the job done.
No thanks necessary.
We'll be working together awhile. I'm sure you'll find a way.
[Flirt] Think of something....
Actually, I have an idea already.
We've got a moment of peace. Close your eyes....
Mia, I don't think this is the moment.
Not right now.
But I--fine. Another time, maybe?
[Flirt] Of course.
Good. Hold still... mm.
Sorry, love. Time to die, along with the traitor.
Mia, you're acting very strange....
This isn't like you.
I don't think you were a secondary target. You said yourself--
That doesn't make sense.
Look, forget it, okay? The important thing is we're both safe.
Let me take a look at you. They use poison sometimes... even a scratch can be nasty.
Anything you can do. I'd rather not die today.
Go ahead.
What kind of poison?
Poison?
Something from one of the native plants. Now, can I take a look?
You should've told me about the poison earlier.
Why didn't you warn me?
You're right. You're right! I'm sorry. Can I have a look, or should we wait 'til you start sweating blood?
I didn't mean to offend you.
Sorry.
Frankly, I'm not sure if I trust you.
I don't know....
Not buying it, are you? Here I thought I had the details right.
You're still going to die. Along with the traitor....
What's wrong with you? I'm trying to help, and you're just making accusations!
Just get it over with.
Fine, do what you want.
Of course. Here we go. The wounds aren't too bad, but--
Now they're worse. You are going to fall; then the traitor will share your fate.
I don't know what's going on, but you're going to explain.
Something's strange here.
I'll tell you nothing. You're going to die--along with the traitor.
Never lie to a professional liar.
Give it up. [Attack]
Ah! You... will fall. Along with the traitor....
Stay back or I'll cut your throat.
